explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the relationship between return and liquidity risk, and the impact of the prospect theory value (PTV) as a moderator variable. The methodologies used include portfolio construction, alpha analysis of factor models, and cross-sectional regression of Fama and Macbeth. None of the provided keywords related to machine learning, neural networks, or other AI techniques are mentioned or implied in the title or abstract. The study is grounded in financial economics and behavioral finance, not in machine learning or related fields.
